path":"/slide[4]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"Defining the construct","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"1.6cm","height":"0.9cm","size":"14pt","bold":"true","color":"57c79a","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[4]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"What a mission statement is","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"2.6cm","height":"2.4cm","size":"32pt","bold":"true","color":"e7b24a","font":"Georgia"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[4]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"Mission statement","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"5.30cm","height":"1.2cm","size":"24pt","bold":"true","color":"e7b24a","font":"Georgia"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[4]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"A concise declaration of an organization's core purpose and reason for existing — what it does, for whom, and to what end.\nIn plain terms: one or two clear sentences saying why we exist.","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"6.60cm","height":"2.8cm","size":"19pt","color":"f3f1ea","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/","type":"slide","props":{"layout":"blank","background":"07241d"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[5]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"What a mission statement is not","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"1.6cm","height":"2.4cm","size":"32pt","bold":"true","color":"e7b24a","font":"Georgia"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[5]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"◆  Not a slogan","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"4.30cm","height":"1.0cm","size":"21pt","bold":"true","color":"f3f1ea","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[5]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"     It is purpose, not a catchy advertising line.","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"5.30cm","height":"1.0cm","size":"16pt","italic":"true","color":"aebfb6","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[5]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"◆  Not a list of goals","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"6.90cm","height":"1.0cm","size":"21pt","bold":"true","color":"f3f1ea","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[5]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"     Goals come later (4.2); the mission is the reason behind them.","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"7.90cm","height":"1.0cm","size":"16pt","italic":"true","color":"aebfb6","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[5]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"◆  Not the vision","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"9.50cm","height":"1.0cm","size":"21pt","bold":"true","color":"f3f1ea","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[5]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"     Vision is the future dream; mission is the present work.","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"10.50cm","height":"1.0cm","size":"16pt","italic":"true","color":"aebfb6","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/","type":"slide","props":{"layout":"blank","background":"07241d"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[6]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"Mission is not the same as vision","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"1.6cm","height":"2.4cm","size":"32pt","bold":"true","color":"e7b24a","font":"Georgia"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[6]","type":"picture","props":{"src":"assets/strategy_s6_0.png","x":"2.20cm","y":"4.30cm","width":"14.23cm","height":"6.19cm"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[6]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"Future-facing and aspirational.","x":"2.20cm","width":"14.23cm","align":"center","y":"10.69cm","height":"1.4cm","size":"13pt","italic":"true","color":"aebfb6","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[6]","type":"picture","props":{"src":"assets/strategy_s6_1.png","x":"17.43cm","y":"4.30cm","width":"14.23cm","height":"6.19cm"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[6]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"Present-facing and active. This is our topic.","x":"17.43cm","width":"14.23cm","align":"center","y":"10.69cm","height":"1.4cm","size":"13pt","italic":"true","color":"aebfb6","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/","type":"slide","props":{"layout":"blank","background":"07241d"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[7]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"A strong mission answers three questions","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"1.6cm","height":"2.4cm","size":"32pt","bold":"true","color":"e7b24a","font":"Georgia"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[7]","type":"picture","props":{"src":"assets/strategy_s7_0.png","x":"4.26cm","y":"4.50cm","width":"25.34cm","height":"5.83cm"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[7]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"Answer all three, in plain language, and the mission is sound.","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"center","y":"10.58cm","height":"1.4cm","size":"14pt","italic":"true","color":"aebfb6","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/","type":"slide","props":{"layout":"blank","background":"07241d"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[8]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"The three parts, up close","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"1.6cm","height":"2.4cm","size":"32pt","bold":"true","color":"e7b24a","font":"Georgia"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[8]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"Who","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"4.30cm","height":"1.2cm","size":"24pt","bold":"true","color":"e7b24a","font":"Georgia"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[8]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"The people we exist to serve — students, families, a community.","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"5.60cm","height":"2.8cm","size":"19pt","color":"f3f1ea","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[8]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"What","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"8.70cm","height":"1.2cm","size":"24pt","bold":"true","color":"e7b24a","font":"Georgia"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide[8]","type":"textbox","props":{"text":"The core service or change we provide to them.","x":"2.2cm","width":"29.47cm","align":"left","y":"10.00cm","height":"2.8cm","size":"19pt","color":"f3f1ea","font":"Calibri"}},{"op":"add","path":"/slide